~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : echo                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : echo <message>

   This is more a fun command than anything really usefull. It 
   simply echoes whatever you write as the text into the room 
   without other users seeing who said it.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
